item.description:
TV Reporter Shot With BB Gun During Live Newscast
At 0:11 you can hear KABC 7 News' correspondent Leanne Suter tell her colleague to "look at the blood." The clip isn't as gruesome on camera as it probably was for the California newscaster who was shot in the hand by a BB pellet during a weather segment. Local police arrested two teenagers who fired the pellets from their backyard.
